	(text "NOTE: LMR38020 pinout (SOIC-8-EP) assumed:\n 1:BOOT  2:VIN  3:EN  4:RT/SYNC\n 5:FB  6:AGND  7:PGND  8:SW  9:EP->GND\nVERIFY against TI SLUSDS8 datasheet before fab."
